Sure Shot				KEY:Archery Talent ~ Sure Shot			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArcheryTalent.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary																												DESC:An archer can use a full-round action to make an attack against an opponent who is up to three range increments away. The opponent is treated as flat-footed against this attack. This attack bypasses any damage reduction the target might have. If the target has uncanny dodge, it retains its damage reduction against this attack.
